import React, { useEffect } from 'react'; import './ProjectSection.css'; import { ToastContainer, toast } from "react-toastify"; import 'react-toastify/dist/ReactToastify.css'; function ProjectSection_french() { const notify1 = () => toast.success("Joined"); useEffect(() => { const checkboxes = document.querySelectorAll('input[type="checkbox"]'); const items = document.getElementById('items').querySelectorAll('li'); function filterItems() { const selectedOptions = Array.from(checkboxes) .filter(checkbox => checkbox.checked) .map(checkbox => checkbox.value); items.forEach(item => { if (selectedOptions.length === 0 || selectedOptions.includes(item.classList[0])) { item.classList.add('show'); } else { item.classList.remove('show'); } }); } // Check initial state of checkboxes filterItems(); checkboxes.forEach(checkbox => checkbox.addEventListener('change', filterItems)); return () => { checkboxes.forEach(checkbox => checkbox.removeEventListener('change', filterItems)); }; }, []); return ( <>
